[oodriveTrackingEvents://<name>]
domain_url = Enter the fully qualified domain name (FQDN) of the server to connect to.
workspace_name = Specify the name of the Oodrive workspace to connect to.
refresh_token = Enter the refresh token obtained during initial authentication.
client_id = Enter the Client ID for your server provided by Oodrive.
client_secret = Enter the Client Secret associated with your Client ID.
enable_app_messages = Check this box to enable the app messages. App messages will be sent to a dedicated source type (oodrive:Tracking:Events-debug), providing detailed information for troubleshooting and diagnostics.